        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Spooner', 3: 'And I suppose it\\'s supposed to express something very... subtle?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 76,
        "ActionId": 76,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'I guess you could say that.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 77,
        "ActionId": 77,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'I\\'ve only scratched the surface of Kowloong culture, but from what I\\'ve seen, Kowloong prefers to use metaphors and euphemisms rather than being direct in their expressions of emotions.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 78,
        "ActionId": 78,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'Humans have a habit of concealing their feelings in their words—ironically, though, their feelings are distorted when expressed through language.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 79,
        "ActionId": 79,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Spooner', 3: 'That\\'s true, language and words... can introduce much more ambiguity than direct communication among mechanoids.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 80,
        "ActionId": 80,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hanying', 3: 'There is much to lose if humans lose their language and writing.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 81,
        "ActionId": 81,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'In Hanying\\'s database in her memory shell, lines that could be used to describe the current scene number in the hundreds.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 82,
        "ActionId": 82,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Even in the same space, at the same time, descriptions of the same entity are, more often than not, different.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 83,
        "ActionId": 83,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'And the writer\\'s emotions—their \"hearts\"—are buried deep within these elusive words.'}"
    },
